    "body": "I don't think we should put effort into supporting commonjs, there are [plenty of workarounds](https://stackoverflow.com/a/75287028/10577550) that can be used.\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nconst prover = (await import('@lodestar/prover')).default\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee [Pure ESM package](https://gist.github.com/sindresorhus/a39789f98801d908bbc7ff3ecc99d99c) for more details.",
